tool_description: Generate images of birds based on text input.
name: DALL-E Bird Images from Text
title: DALL-E Bird Images from Text

api_list.name: generate
api_list.description:
Generates a bird image from text returning the image in base64.

Parameters:
`text`: Text describing the bird

Returns:
`base64img`: Image encoded in base64. See the About section for loading base64.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://dall-e-bird-images-from-text.p.rapidapi.com/0.5.0"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "dall-e-bird-images-from-text.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
